OL,6,FTV schedules are now back to normal   
OL,7,Ffollowing the period of mourning which
OL,8,Ffollowed the death of HM The Queen. But
OL,9,Fthere will be a legacy which is likely
OL,10,Fto be felt for several days.          
OL,12,FThe main commercial channels suspended
OL,13,Fall advertising in the immediate      
OL,14,Faftermath of The Queen's death.       
OL,16,FThrough the period of mourning, there 
OL,17,Fwas no advertising around programmes  
OL,18,Fconcerning Her Majesty's death or the 
OL,19,Ffuneral. Indeed advertising is        
OL,20,Fspecifically forbidden during formal  
OL,21,FRoyal events.                         
OL,3,CCommercial channels play catch-up with
OL,4,Cadverts                               
OL,22,                                   G1/6
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}  S      G
