OL,6,FFor instance there is now a full 12   
OL,7,Fminutes of advertising in the 3pm hour
OL,8,Fand an extra 4 minute break just before
OL,9,Fthe ITV Evening News at 6.30pm.       
OL,11,FThe break before 9pm has also been    
OL,12,Freconfigured  generally 90 seconds of
OL,13,Fadvertising Is running before 9pm and 
OL,14,F90 seconds afterwards. Before, the    
OL,15,Fbreak normally only lasted 90 seconds 
OL,16,Fin total.                             
OL,18,FThis is being done, it seems, to allow
OL,19,Fan extra break of around 4 minutes    
OL,20,Fbefore News at Ten which has          
OL,21,Ftemporarily been billed at 10.05pm.   
OL,3,CCommercial channels play catch-up with
OL,4,Cadverts                               
OL,22,                                   G3/6
