PS,c000
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F343A1664222673
OL,6,FThe main reason for moving things round
OL,7,Fso much is to ensure that no clock hour
OL,8,Fcontains more than 12 minutes of      
OL,9,Fadverts.                              
OL,11,FWhile this is only temporary, it comes
OL,12,Fas Ofcom considers whether to allow   
OL,13,FITV, Channel 4 and Channel 5 to run as
OL,14,Fmany adverts as other channels.       
OL,16,FIf there if no adverse public reaction,
OL,17,Fit will suggest that the public might 
OL,18,Faccept a permanent increase.          
OL,3,CCommercial channels play catch-up with
OL,4,Cadverts                               
OL,22,                                   G4/6
